{"tid":2260370,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李國章：申作軍已表明非中共黨員　校委會滿意澄清","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T16:45:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":249,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"93c58e5e7ef4fd95d30075d7478572820bae240b","tid":2260370,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"港大校委會主席李國章就任命決定發聲明，指候任副校長申作軍，表明他不是中國共產黨員，校委會滿意其澄清。<br />\n<br />\n李國章在聲明指，遴選工作經由全球物色適當人選，審視和諮詢過程詳盡嚴謹，唯一目的是為大學招攬最優秀的人才。<br />\n<br />\n對於近期就兩位副校長人選申作軍及宮鵬的背景有諸多傳聞和猜測，二人已特意作出澄清，包括申作軍已表明他不是中國共產黨員；也不是黨委成員。<br />\n<br />\n校委會對二人澄清表示滿意，認爲所有指控皆不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410667&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=20adf836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410667&h=97841518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410667</a>"},{"pid":"6956d2d75173de6ef8b56ee1e51f0d44cec1f4c8","tid":2260370,"uid":133,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"表明就係呀<br />\n有冇撚fact check 呀 ？"},{"pid":"18df54db146a227303be99f403ab9a5065495881","tid":2260370,"uid":76804,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"齋聽個名已經聞到陣地溝油味啦<br />\n同我講唔係黨員?<br />\n當人傻既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2910ecd4d892c471aa49d5c15f460117c820eb68","tid":2260370,"uid":264245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"係唔係派膠"},{"pid":"d681849f4ce2439eb21c48f9241531ef4951f2ee","tid":2260370,"uid":1275,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"93c58e5e7ef4fd95d30075d7478572820bae240b","tid":2260370,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":